  "screens": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "进入交易后，你会先遇到两个方向。",
        "涨，或者跌。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "如果你先买，期待以后卖得更贵。",
        "这叫 **<term id=\"long_position\">多头仓位</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "long_position"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "long_position"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "多头最朴素的逻辑就是：",
        "低买，高卖。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "long_position"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "如果你先卖，期待以后再更便宜地买回来。",
        "这叫 **<term id=\"short_position\">空头仓位</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "short_position"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "short_position"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "空头的赚钱逻辑刚好反过来。",
        "先高卖，再低买。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "short_position"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "现在做个一秒判断。",
        "价格上涨更伤哪一边？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "如果价格继续上涨，哪一边通常更难受？",
        "options": [
          "多头",
          "空头",
          "两边一样"
        ],
        "answer": 1,
        "explanation": "空头是先卖后买，价格往上走会让回补更贵。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "但空头还有一层操作细节。",
        "你未必真的先持有资产。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "这时候就会出现 **<term id=\"short_selling\">卖空</term>**。",
        "先借来，再卖出。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "short_selling"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "short_selling"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "之后如果价格下跌，",
        "你再买回来还给出借方。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "short_selling"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "听上去很优雅。",
        "但风险也更凶。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "因为价格理论上可以一直涨。",
        "所以卖空的亏损空间并没有天然上限。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "short_selling"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "这里先别背流程。",
        "先抓住风险方向。"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "卖空最直观的核心风险是什么？",
        "options": [
          "价格持续上涨",
          "价格完全不动",
          "成交量太低"
        ],
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "价格越涨，回补成本越高，所以卖空会越来越痛。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "再往市场微观结构里走一步。",
        "你会看到 **<term id=\"order_book\">订单簿</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "order_book"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "order_book"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "它不是历史成交表。",
        "它是“大家此刻想怎么交易”的队列。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "order_book"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "卖方一侧叫 **<term id=\"ask_book\">卖盘簿</term>**。",
        "买方一侧叫 **<term id=\"bid_book\">买盘簿</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "ask_book",
        "bid_book"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "ask_book",
        "bid_book"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "离成交最近的位置，",
        "叫 **<term id=\"top_of_book\">盘口顶端</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "top_of_book"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "top_of_book"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "挂单层级越长、越厚，",
        "通常说明 **<term id=\"market_depth\">市场深度</term>** 越高。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "market_depth"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "market_depth"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "如果把数量从盘口顶端一路累加，",
        "你看到的就是 **<term id=\"cumulative_book\">累计订单簿</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "cumulative_book"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "cumulative_book"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "现在把几个词排好。",
        "哪个最靠近“马上能成交”？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "下面哪个概念最直接指向离成交最近的位置？",
        "options": [
          "市场深度",
          "盘口顶端",
          "累计订单簿"
        ],
        "answer": 1,
        "explanation": "盘口顶端就是最高买价和最低卖价所在的位置。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "这一步真正想让你看见的是：",
        "仓位方向决定你怎么赌，<term id=\"order_book\">订单簿</term> 决定市场怎么接。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "order_book"
      ]
    }
  ],
